title: Mid/Low Diamond ADC LF team

embed.description: Check your Summoner statistics, MMR, realtime spectate and using powerful global LoL Charts!

body:
Can play everyday and I'm very active. I am quite positive and don't tend to rage. I've played in competitive teams before.
I main Tristana/Vayne/Miss Fortune but can play most others.
I'd prefer a high elo team but it's not a complete necessity. 
If it's a problem for any teams I'm 15 years old. 
If you want to trial me or something that's cool, just add DeathGod64. I'm on all day everyday so I should respond quickly unless I'm watching something on YouTube/Twitch ^_^
